transcript:

Hello? Awaz aa rahi hai sir? Hello?
Ji haan. Sir, mai Himeera baat kar rahi hu. Abhi baat ho rahi thi sir aapse. Maine number share kiya hai aapko dekhiye. Aapko WhatsApp aa gaya kya?
Mai dekhta hu baad me. Hello?
Haa, ek baar. Mai baad me dekhta hu.
Ek minute dekh lijiye, number bhi save kar lijiye kyuki baad me kuch issue na ho na. Aur plus mapping vagera ke correction ka mai keh rahi thi. Ki products me to kuch add addition hi karana hai na sir abhi apna?
Hai na? Koi kuch add ya nahi karana? Nahi, kuch nahi karana.
Kuch nahi karana hai. Baki mujhe changes ki requirement to lagti thi ki mai apni site se jo lag raha hai, mai vo filhal ke liye kar de rahi hu. Thik hai? Koi dikkat to nahi hai na sir aapko?
Thik hai, aapko jo lage aap kar dijiye.
Thik hai, mai apni site se kar de rahi hu. Koi baat nahi sir. Okay.
